## 🚀 Projects

### In-Line Sprue Regrinding and Circular Integration
**VALEO · February 2026**

A circular economy initiative targeting waste reduction in the injection molding process.

- Strategically selected injection presses based on material consumption costs and workshop logistics
- Validated mechanical properties and injection parameters for specific regrind-to-virgin ratios to ensure production quality using recycled content

> **Impact:** Enabled sustainable production cycles by formally qualifying recycled material use in high-quality components.

---

### Injection Cycle Time and Process Optimization
**VALEO · December 2025**

A systematic optimization of the injection cycle to increase throughput without capital expenditure.

- Refined mold kinematics for faster and more reliable operation
- Analyzed and adjusted injection phase parameters to minimize idle time

> **Impact:** Achieved up to **15% reduction in average idle time**, directly improving machine throughput.

---

### Lean Manufacturing: Muda Hunting & SMED Implementation
**VALEO · October 2025**

A comprehensive lean manufacturing project targeting operational waste and press changeover inefficiency.

- Eliminated operational waste (Muda) by auditing operator control methods and re-engineering task sequences
- Engineered rapid setup systems for 400T & 100T presses using magnetic/hydraulic clamping, multi-coupling water manifolds, and robotic EOAT quick-change plates

> **Impact:** Documented changeover time reductions of up to **30 minutes per changeover**.

---

### KPI Performance Tracking System
**VALEO · September 2025**

Designed and deployed a custom KPI dashboard for real-time production performance monitoring.

- Tracks downtime, changeover durations, and micro-stops in real time
- Enables data-driven decision-making for continuous improvement teams

---

### Material Characterization of Recycled Plastics for Injection Molding
**Final Year Project · June 2025**

An academic-industrial research project investigating the viability of recycled plastics in injection-molded automotive components.

- Analyzed mechanical behavior of various recycled plastic grades
